<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>ZPanel: Email Update Request</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Hello, {{name}}!</h1>
    <p>We have received a request to update the email address associated with your account on the ZPanel platform.</p>
    <p><strong>Current Email:</strong> {{oldEmail}}</p>
    <p><strong>New Email:</strong> {{newEmail}}</p>
    <br/>
    <p>If you initiated this request, no further action is required. The change will take effect once the new email verification process is complete.</p>
    <p>If you did not request this change, please contact our support team immediately at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a>.</p>
    <br/>
    <p>Thank you for using ZPanel!</p>
    <br/>
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>The ZPanel Team</p>
</body>
</html>